title: (Mon Full) Bobby Brought Up A Listener At The Opry To Sing and Didn’t Expect What Happened Next + Lunchbox’s Birthday! + Did We Win Anything in the Lottery?
itunes:title: (Mon Full) Bobby Brought Up A Listener At The Opry To Sing and Didn’t Expect What Happened Next + Lunchbox’s Birthday! + Did We Win Anything in the Lottery?
description:
Bobby got a tweet from a listener on Friday and he decided to bring her up at the Opry to sing a duet. He had no idea she could sing and was blown away by what happened next. We celebrate Lunchbox’s birthday! He shares if we won any money from our lottery pool even though no one won the jackpot. Do we go in again?

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
